<i>adverb</i>: 철저히 [철쩌히], 철두철미 [철뚜철미], 말짱히 [말짱히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>철저히 [철쩌히]</dt><br>
<dd>perfectly; immaculately; thoroughly</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하는 데 있어서 매우 조심하여 부족함이 없이 완벽하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being complete without flaws because one is very careful about something.</dd><br>
<dt>철두철미 [철뚜철미]</dt><br>
<dd>perfectly; immaculately; impeccably</dd><br>
<dd>처음부터 끝까지 빈틈이나 부족함이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>Completely without flaws or defects.</dd><br>
<dt>말짱히 [말짱히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. spotlessly; impeccably; unhurt</dd><br>
<dd>흠이나 다친 곳 등이 없고 온전한 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being intact without flaws, wounds, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. sanely; soberly</dd><br>
<dd>정신이 맑고 또렷한 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one's consciousness is clear and distinct.</dd><br>
<dd>3. neatly; immaculately</dd><br>
<dd>지저분한 것이 없고 말끔하고 깨끗한 상태로.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being tidy and clear without dirty things.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>